reviewText: Chichay and Joaquin continue their saga of fighting for their young love. Highlights of this dvd: the Crillon Ball. The ball where the high society snooties dress up and meet. Guess who is working at the ball? Chichay! One of the highlights of the series where Joaquin defies his mother once again to  prove his love for Chichay and this time, in front of high society!
